<br>
Aragorn the Ranger from LOTR.  If I made a Human Ranger named Aragorn, they should probably change it.  If I made an Iksar Shadow Knight named Arragoren, it should probably be left alone.  Its obviously NOT an imitation of the character. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/urazzlerdazzler.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Razzlerdazzler</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 123<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/11/01 4:42:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=40.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Inappropriate name list...</span><hr size=1> What are you the name nazi now my god go play the damned game and leave others alone. <p><img src="http://1johnny.freeservers.com/Razzler.jpg" border="0">
